{"type":null,"faqId":15389,"title":"榮耀3C 4G版(H30-L02)_郵箱設置","answer":"<p style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'PMingLiU','serif'; MARGIN-LEFT: 0cm; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0cm\">添加<span>Email</span>帳戶</p>\n<p style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'PMingLiU','serif'; MARGIN-LEFT: 0cm; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0cm\">進入 <span>設置</span><span> &gt; </span><span>帳戶<span> &gt; </span>添加帳戶</span>。選擇<span>電子郵件</span>添加<span>Email</span>帳戶，選擇<span>公司</span>添加<span>Exchange</span>帳戶。</p>\n<p style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'PMingLiU','serif'; MARGIN-LEFT: 0cm; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0cm\"><span><img alt=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/18d35_utzxn.jpg\" width=\"720\" height=\"1280\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20141007151709909001.jpg\"><img alt=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/18d36_1ttxx.jpg\" width=\"720\" height=\"1280\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20141007151709969002.jpg\"><img alt=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/18d37_1ripg.jpg\" width=\"720\" height=\"1280\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20141007151710394003.jpg\"><img alt=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/18d38_2fkgn.jpg\" width=\"720\" height=\"1280\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20141007151710880004.jpg\"><img alt=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/18d39_vrmvz.jpg\" width=\"720\" height=\"1280\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20141007151710105005.jpg\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'PMingLiU','serif'; MARGIN-LEFT: 0cm; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0cm\"><span><span>-- </span>手動設置：</span></p>\n<p style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'PMingLiU','serif'; MARGIN-LEFT: 0cm; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0cm\">帳戶設置介面<span> &gt; </span>輸入帳號和密碼。</p>\n<p style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'PMingLiU','serif'; MARGIN-LEFT: 0cm; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0cm\">點擊手動設置。</p>\n<p style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'PMingLiU','serif'; MARGIN-LEFT: 0cm; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0cm\">點擊<span>POP3</span>，進入接收伺服器設置介面。</p>\n<p style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'PMingLiU','serif'; MARGIN-LEFT: 0cm; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0cm\">點擊下一步，進入外發伺服器設置介面。</p>\n<p style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'PMingLiU','serif'; MARGIN-LEFT: 0cm; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0cm\">點擊下一步，進入郵件接收設置介面，可選擇收件箱檢查頻率。</p>\n<p style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'PMingLiU','serif'; MARGIN-LEFT: 0cm; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0cm\">點擊下一步，進入設置電子郵件介面為此帳戶創建名稱和您的姓名。</p>\n<p style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'PMingLiU','serif'; MARGIN-LEFT: 0cm; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0cm\">點擊下一步，完成登錄並進入收件箱介面。</p>","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":201,"languageName":"tr_CN","faqCode":"7706","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1412666288000,"seriesProductName":"H30-L02","visitedTimes":150,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"H30-L02,H30,3C,3C-LTE","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}